<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>页面未找到 | 云朵创客空间</title>
    <meta name="description" content="您访问的页面不存在或已移动。" />
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        --bg: #f5f7f2;
        --panel: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
        --text: #163022;
        --muted: #5b6f63;
        --accent: #1f7a5a;
        --accent-strong: #14523c;
        --border: rgba(22, 48, 34, 0.1);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        padding: 24px;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(120, 189, 158, 0.28), transparent 35%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #fcfdf8 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: "PingFang SC", "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      }

      main {
        width: min(720px, 100%);
        padding: 40px 32px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 28px;
        background: var(--panel);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(25, 65, 47, 0.12);
      }

      p.kicker {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 7vw, 4.6rem);
        line-height: 0.95;
      }

      p.copy {
        margin: 18px 0 0;
        max-width: 34rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 28px;
      }

      a {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 46px;
        padding: 0 18px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      a.primary {
        background: var(--accent);
        color: white;
      }

      a.primary:hover {
        background: var(--accent-strong);
      }

      a.secondary {
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        color: var(--text);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <p class="kicker">404</p>
      <h1>页面未找到</h1>
      <p class="copy">您访问的页面不存在、已移动，或者链接地址输入有误。可以返回首页继续浏览课程与指南内容。</p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="primary" href="/">返回首页</a>
        <a class="secondary" href="javascript:history.back()">返回上一页</a>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
